videos.description: Darrynton Evans takes the kickoff 97 yards and is stopped just short of the goal line to set up a Marcus Williams Jr. 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: App State 97-yard kick return sets up 1-yard TD

videos.description: QB Zac Thomas takes a draw 25 yards for an Appalachian State touchdown and a 14-6 lead over Louisiana.
videos.headline: App State's Thomas goes untouched on 25-yard TD

videos.description: Louisiana-Lafayette's Andre Nunez keeps it and runs for an 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Ragin Cajuns' QB keeps and runs for an 8-yard TD
